we get to introduce you to Positron. This is a very early stage project that was

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:18.040
just made public about six weeks ago and I am the first of seven speakers in this

00:00:18.040 --> 00:00:22.840
session. We're each going to speak for roughly ten minutes and at the end we

