01:15:15.779 --> 01:15:18.100
like your desktop and connect to Databricks

01:15:18.100 --> 01:15:20.419
for data access or Spark compute.

01:15:21.299 --> 01:15:24.819
Posit Workbench would add on managed credentials,

01:15:24.819 --> 01:15:25.779
which is an IDE,

01:15:25.779 --> 01:15:27.459
and then you can run Posit Workbench

